{"id":996,"date":"2010-02-15T08:00:27","date_gmt":"2010-02-15T00:00:27","guid":{"rendered":"http://xbeta.info/?p=996"},"modified":"2010-02-15T08:00:27","modified_gmt":"2010-02-15T00:00:27","slug":"ooo-news","status":"publish","link":"https://xbeta.info/ooo-news.htm","title":{"rendered":"OpenOffice.org 3.2 Final 已发布，中文版稍后"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>　　OpenOffice.org 我用得并不多（工作文档全用MS Office，个人文档基本用txt和html），也并不主动推荐普通用户选用OOo——但非常支持它。所以，在重大消息方面保持跟进，算作宣传。最近的一次应用是 <a href=\"http://www.newsmth.net/bbstcon.php?board=OfficeSoft&#038;gid=91014\">OpenOffice 挽救 MS Excel 2007 文档</a>。<br />\n 　　言归正传：<a href=\"http://www.openoffice.org/\">OpenOffice.org</a> 3.2 在历经5个RC之后，Final 已经发布，在<a href=\"http://download.openoffice.org/\">这里下载</a>。但官方中文版尚未更新。<br />\n 　　急需中文的用户可以考虑 3.2.0 RC5 (候选版5)：http://ftp5.gwdg.de/pub/openoffice/extended/3.2.0rc5/<br />\n（如果选择英文版，再安装中文包，会有一些问题。）</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://img.xbeta.info/ooo-3.2.png\" alt=\"OOo\" /></p>\n<h2>OpenOffice.org 3.2 新特性</h2>\n<p>总体：<br />\n启动更快<br />\nODF支持<br />\n对专有格式的支持<br />\n支持基于 Postscript 的开放字体</p>\n<p>writer:<br />\n对Mediawiki 的支持改为扩展形式</p>\n<p>Calc：<br />\n单元格边框支持多选<br />\n自动填充更加智能，如10.0.0.1 is followed by 10.0.0.2<br />\n改进排序功能<br />\n改进单元格合并<br />\n复杂的复制粘贴<br />\n改进统计功能<br />\n公式中保留换行符<br />\n文本到数字的自动转换<br />\n改进过滤功能<br />\n直接与间接引用切换增强<br />\n增强CONVERT_ADD新函数 UNICODE and UNICHAR functions</p>\n<p>Draw与Impress：<br />\n新风格的注释，便于协作<br />\n支持页码</p>\n<p>Math, Base略</p>\n<p>Chart：<br />\n新图类型<br />\n提高可用性<br />\n增强数据标签<br />\n亚洲字符格式支持</p>\n<p>国际化：略</p>\n<p>更多参见：<a href=\"http://wiki.services.openoffice.org/wiki/Features#Features_planned_for_OOo_3.2_.28November_2009.29\">Features_planned_for_OOo_3.2</a>, <a href=\"http://www.openoffice.org/dev_docs/features/3.2/rc2.html\">OpenOffice.org 3.2 New Features</a></iframe></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>　　OpenOffice.org 我用得并不多（工作文档全用MS Office，个人文档基本用txt和html [&hellip;]</p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":["1 文本办公","未分类"],"tags":["OOo/LibreOffice","all"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/996"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/types/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/users/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/comments?post=996"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/posts/996/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/media?parent=996"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/categories?post=996"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https://xbeta.info/wp-json/wp/v2/tags?post=996"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https://api.w.org/{rel}","templated":true}]},"wp_type":"post"}